The paper deals with approximation algorithms for facility location problems, which are typically studied in the areas of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), game theory (cs.GT), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The use of LP-rounding and clustering techniques also suggests a connection to optimization (cs.DS, cs.DM) and approximation algorithms (cs.DS, cs.AI).
